## 🐛 Bug Report

When I iterate with `eachCell`, `numFmt` cant be used.

Lib version: 4.1.0

## Steps To Reproduce

```javascript
const wb = new ExcelJS.Workbook();
const read = await wb.xlsx.readFile(path.join(__dirname, '../public/report/template_historis_wadiah.xlsx')).catch(() => null);
const worksheet = wb.getWorksheet(1);

data.forEach((datum, index) => {
      const dataWorkRow = 6 + index;
      const insertedRow = worksheet.insertRow(dataWorkRow, [datum.patient.no_reg, datum.patient.name, datum.patient.unit, datum.patient.payment.insurance_name, datum.total_wadiah, datum.total_pengambilan, datum.total_saldo, datum.status], 'i');
      
      worksheet.getRow(dataWorkRow).eachCell((cell) => {
        cell.font.bold = false;
        cell.numFmt = '#,##0;[Red]\-#,##0';
      });
      insertedRow.commit();
});
```

## The expected behaviour:

Expected cell can be formatted.
